---
title: Pork Tenderloin and Veggie Tray-Bake with Creamy Mustard Sauce
description: Nothing says comfort food like pan-roasted pork tenderloin and a hearty root veggie medley of potatoes, carrots and onions, all topped with a drizzle of rich mustard-sage sauce. You'll be licking your plate clean!
